        public <T> T getSlaveMap​(ResourceLocation name,
                         java.lang.Class<T> type)
        从接口复制的说明: IForgeRegistry
        Retrieve the slave map of type T from the registry. Slave maps are maps which are dependent on registry content in some way.
        指定者:

        类型参数:
        T - Type to return
        参数:
        name - The name of the slavemap
        type - The type
        返回:
